566
00:40:10,880 --> 00:40:13,792
You know what she's called?

567
00:40:15,800 --> 00:40:17,677
She's called...

568
00:40:17,840 --> 00:40:20,115
...Incontinentia.

569
00:40:22,120 --> 00:40:24,395
Incontinentia Buttocks. Shut up!

570
00:40:24,560 --> 00:40:26,073
What is all this?

571
00:40:26,240 --> 00:40:29,676
I've had enough of this rowdy-rebel,
sniggering behaviour!

572
00:40:29,840 --> 00:40:32,957
Silence!
You call yourselves centurion guards?

573
00:40:33,160 --> 00:40:36,675
Seize him! Seize him!
Blow your noses and seize him!

574
00:42:29,600 --> 00:42:32,990
You lucky bastard.

575
00:42:47,920 --> 00:42:50,354
And the beast's head
shall be huge and black...

576
00:42:50,520 --> 00:42:54,877
...and the eyes. They're of red,
