599
00:44:23,520 --> 00:44:24,953
-I haven't got time--
-Give it back.

600
00:44:25,120 --> 00:44:26,792
-No, no, no, I just paid you.
-Burt.

601
00:44:26,960 --> 00:44:28,951
-Yeah?
-This bloke won't haggle.

602
00:44:29,120 --> 00:44:31,680
-Won't haggle?!
-All right, do we have to?

603
00:44:31,840 --> 00:44:34,513
-Now look, I want 20 for that.
