604
00:44:34,680 --> 00:44:36,989
-Are you telling me that's not worth 20?
-No.

605
00:44:37,160 --> 00:44:39,469
Look. Feel the quality,
that's none of your goat.

606
00:44:39,640 --> 00:44:42,359
-All right, I'll give you 19.
