607
00:44:42,520 --> 00:44:44,988
-What?
-Haggle properly, this isn't worth 19.

608
00:44:45,160 --> 00:44:47,799
-Well, you just said it was worth 20.
-Oh, dear, oh, dear.

609
00:44:47,960 --> 00:44:49,996
-Come on, haggle.
-All right, I'll give you 10.

610
00:44:50,160 --> 00:44:53,311
That's more like it.
