-That's what you told me to say!

618
00:45:12,800 --> 00:45:14,870
-Oh, dear.
-Tell me what to say, please!

619
00:45:16,040 --> 00:45:17,792
-Offer me 14.
-I'll give you 14.

620
00:45:18,080 --> 00:45:20,833
-He's offering me 14 for this!
-Fifteen!

621
00:45:21,040 --> 00:45:24,112
Seventeen. My last word, I won't take
a penny less, or strike me dead.

622
00:45:24,320 --> 00:45:25,912
-Sixteen.
-Done.

623
00:45:26,560 --> 00:45:27,913
