if it's worth a shekel!

632
00:45:46,520 --> 00:45:49,512
-You just gave it to me for nothing.
-Yes, but it's worth 10.

633
00:45:49,880 --> 00:45:51,279
All right, all right.

634
00:45:53,920 --> 00:45:57,071
No, no, no, no, it's not worth 10,
you're supposed to argue.

635
00:45:57,240 --> 00:45:59,549
"Ten for that? You must be mad!"

636
00:46:02,280 --> 00:46:05,431
Oh, well. One born every minute.

637
00:46:05,880 --> 00:46:07,472
-Daniel.
-Daniel.

638
00:46:07,640 --> 00:46:08,675
-Job.
-Job.

639
00:46:08,840 --> 00:46:10,273
-Job.
-Joshua.

