647
00:46:28,080 --> 00:46:31,959
Siblings, let us not be down on it.

648
00:46:32,120 --> 00:46:36,716
One total catastrophe like this
is just the beginning!

649
00:46:36,880 --> 00:46:39,678
Their glorious deaths
shall unite us all in a--

650
00:46:39,880 --> 00:46:41,950
Look out!

651
00:46:52,400 --> 00:46:53,992
Hello?

652
00:46:54,160 --> 00:46:55,832
Matthias?

653
00:46:56,520 --> 00:46:59,478
