655
00:47:04,000 --> 00:47:05,149
-Stan?
-Piss off.

656
00:47:05,320 --> 00:47:07,675
-Yeah, piss off.
-Bugger off.

657
00:47:10,760 --> 00:47:12,671
Shit!

658
00:47:12,840 --> 00:47:14,671
Coming.

659
00:47:19,200 --> 00:47:22,636
Yea, verily at that time,
which is written in the Book of Obadiah...

660
00:47:22,840 --> 00:47:26,958
