of Passover!

978
01:07:39,760 --> 01:07:42,911
My friend Biggus Dickus has come
all the way from Rome to hear it!

979
01:07:43,080 --> 01:07:45,594
-Hail Caesar!
-Hail Caesar!

980
01:07:46,320 --> 01:07:48,515
