1058
01:12:29,400 --> 01:12:31,595
Oh, no, sir!

1059
01:12:32,880 --> 01:12:37,032
Very well. I shall release Roderick!

1060
01:12:37,200 --> 01:12:39,031
Sir, we don't have a Roderick either.

1061
01:12:39,200 --> 01:12:42,192
-No Roger, no Roderick?
-Sorry, sir.

1062
01:12:42,360 --> 01:12:46,956
