1087
01:14:04,560 --> 01:14:08,189
How many have come through?

1088
01:14:11,320 --> 01:14:13,880
-Oh, dear.
-I make it 90--

1089
01:14:14,040 --> 01:14:15,598
Ninety--

1090
01:14:15,760 --> 01:14:17,239
Ninety--

1091
01:14:18,360 --> 01:14:20,191
Ninety-six, sir.

1092
01:14:20,360 --> 01:14:22,749
It's such a senseless waste
of human life, isn't it?

1093
01:14:22,920 --> 01:14:24,990
No, sir!

1094
01:14:25,160 --> 01:14:29,073
Not with these b--
Bastards, sir!

1095
01:14:34,800 --> 01:14:36,950
Crucifixion's too good for them, sir.

1096
01:14:37,120 --> 01:14:39,554
I don't think you could
say it's good, it's nasty!

1097
01:14:39,720 --> 01:14:41,756
It's not as n--

1098
01:14:44,560 --> 01:14:47,791
Not as nasty as something
I just thought up, sir.

1099
01:14:47,960 --> 01:14:50,952
-Now, crucifixion?
-ls there someone I could speak to?

1100
01:14:51,120 --> 01:14:54,351
-Well....
-I know where to get it if you want it.

1101
01:14:54,520 --> 01:14:58,513
-What?
-Don't worry about him, sir. He's de--

1102
01:15:01,000 --> 01:15:03,389
He's deaf and mad, sir.

1103
01:15:03,560 --> 01:15:05,152
Well, how did he get the job?

1104
01:15:05,320 --> 01:15:07,595
Bloody Pilate's pet, sir!

1105
01:15:07,760 --> 01:15:11,719
Get a move on, big nose! There's people
waiting to be crucified out here!

1106
01:15:12,200 --> 01:15:13,952
Could I see a lawyer or someone?

1107
01:15:14,120 --> 01:15:16,111
-Do you have a lawyer?
-No, but I'm a Roman.

1108
01:15:16,280 --> 01:15:18,589
How about a retrial?
We've got plenty of time.

1109
01:15:19,080 --> 01:15:21,196
-Shut up, you!
-Miserable, bloody Romans!

1110
01:15:21,360 --> 01:15:23,430
No sense of humour.

1111
01:15:23,600 --> 01:15:24,589
Sorry, bit of a hurry.

1112
01:15:24,760 --> 01:15:29,038
Can you go straight out,
line on the left, one cross each? Now....

1113
01:15:37,560 --> 01:15:40,552
Was it something I said?

1114
01:15:42,160 --> 01:15:46,039
Silence!

1115
01:15:46,200 --> 01:15:50,079
