1116
01:15:54,080 --> 01:15:56,958
He ranks as high as any in Rome!

1117
01:16:01,440 --> 01:16:02,873
Crucifixion party?

1118
01:16:04,880 --> 01:16:05,869
Morning.

1119
01:16:06,040 --> 01:16:10,238
Now, we will be on show as we go through
the town, so let's not let the side down!

1120
01:16:10,400 --> 01:16:13,472
Keep in a line, three lengths
between you and the man in front...

1121
01:16:13,640 --> 01:16:15,392
...and a good, steady pace.

1122
01:16:15,560 --> 01:16:19,189
Crosses over your left shoulders,
and if you keep your backs hard up...

1123
01:16:19,360 --> 01:16:22,716
