you'll be there in no time.

1124
01:16:22,880 --> 01:16:23,949
All right, centurion!

1125
01:16:24,120 --> 01:16:26,270
Crucifixion party!

1126
01:16:26,440 --> 01:16:28,351
Wait for it.

1127
01:16:28,520 --> 01:16:30,795
Crucifixion party!

1128
01:16:30,960 --> 01:16:34,919
