1129
01:16:38,080 --> 01:16:40,469
You lucky bastards!

1130
01:16:41,840 --> 01:16:45,389
You lucky, jabby bastards!

1131
01:16:53,440 --> 01:16:56,238
Let me shoulder your burden, brother!

1132
01:16:56,400 --> 01:16:59,472
Thank you.

1133
01:16:59,640 --> 01:17:02,552
-Hey! Hey!
-What do you think you're doing?

1134
01:17:02,720 --> 01:17:03,755
