That'll teach you a lesson!

1137
01:17:13,040 --> 01:17:15,110
All right!

1138
01:17:15,280 --> 01:17:17,475
I will give you one more chance!

1139
01:17:17,640 --> 01:17:23,590
This time I want to hear
no Rubens, no Reginalds...

1140
01:17:23,760 --> 01:17:26,718
...no Rudolph the Red-nosed Reindeers.

1141
01:17:26,880 --> 01:17:28,791
No Spencer Tracys!

1142
01:17:28,960 --> 01:17:30,791
Or we shall release no one!

1143
01:17:30,960 --> 01:17:32,552
Release Brian!

1144
01:17:32,720 --> 01:17:34,073
Yeah, that's a good one!

1145
01:17:34,240 --> 01:17:38,756
Release Brian! Release Brian!

1146
01:17:39,680 --> 01:17:41,477
Very well! That's it!

1147
01:17:41,640 --> 01:17:43,870
-Sir, we have got a Brian, sir.
-What?

1148
01:17:44,040 --> 01:17:49,068
-You just sent him for crucifixion, sir!
-Wait! Wait! We do have a Brian.

1149
01:17:49,240 --> 01:17:52,357
-Well, go and free him, straight away!
-Yes, sir. Yes, sir.

1150
01:17:54,640 --> 01:18:00,317
Very well. I shall release Brian!

1151
01:18:03,720 --> 01:18:06,109
-Get a move on, there!
-Or what?

1152
01:18:06,280 --> 01:18:07,508
